	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=140525"><span id=" ">Darkmatil</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">86 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Default [2.37]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>The proc is called Wandering Mind recourse, which is the same as the lvl 39 enchanter spell. It's a DOT that drains 120 mana in 20 ticks.&nbsp;&nbsp;And yes, the target has to be a caster and have mana for the proc to work.  If they are not, it will say &quot;Your target has no mana to affect&quot; when the weapon should proc.<br/><br/>Oh, and the picture on this page shows a damage bonus of 11.  They must have nerfed it, cause it no longer has any damage bonus.  Still has AC though.  A very nice weapon i've enjoyed having, and i'm sure I will keep using it until i get my epic.</p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Darkmatil Bonebringer<br/>70th level Wraith<br/>Cazic Thule</td></tr>
